AUSTRIAN AIRLINES
HOW TO TAKE ADVANTAGE OF
OUR INTERNATIONAL NETWORK
3 EAST 48 STREET, NEW YORK, N. Y. 10017 • PLAZA 2-8388

MODERN FLEET
AUA Austrian Airlines operates a modern
fleet of five Caravelle VI-R jetliners, each
carrying up to 74 passengers and a crew of
six (including four hostesses). Soaring high
above the local weather, the sleek Caravelles
offer their passengers breathtaking views of
the majestic Alps on many of AUA's inter-
national routes.
Fast, dependable service is also provided
by AUA's fleet of six prop-jetliners, including
four 56-passenger Vickers Viscounts with pic-
ture windows and two new 44-passenger HS
748 Belvederes, used primarily for domestic
flights inside Austria and for certain short-
route international flights. All AUA aircraft
feature four or five-across seating for maxi-
mum comfort without crowding. Choose AUA
now for fast, convenient intra-European travel.
